computational environment into a familiar mental landscape! This is a tool \
that makes documents, ", "Text"],
 StyleBox["living", "Text",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 StyleBox[" documents of computational data with human commentary. This tool \
should be as familiar as ", "Text"],
